resources.description: The map includes estimates for calculations of degree days of heating in annual and monthly base. The prices have been determined with method of linear regression in a table 900 x 900 metres having as data of entry analytic measurements by 47 meteorological stations of National Meteorological Service for years 1997 - 2002. The statistical calculations are indicative provided that they depend from the adoption of big number of parameters.
resources.name: Chart of heating degree-days of Greece
